QuantumShield is open source and MIT licensed.

125
00:10:53,991 --> 00:10:56,071
To explore the implementation:

126
00:10:56,071 --> 00:10:57,561
Let's explore Roadmap.

127
00:10:57,561 --> 00:11:00,241
QuantumShield is actively developed.

128
